videos.title: The Pro Tour Winning Deck that Bored Opponents to Death
videos.description:
Normally you win a game of Magic: the Gathering by getting your opponent's life total to zero, but this is the story of the Pro Tour winning deck that looked to bore its opponents into death...

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
